  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FC0D2AD0-2209-0135-E94B-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To delete the contact method, click the <strong>Delete</strong> icon.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="confirm_deletion" data-step-uuid="2abd99bf-5a26-4694-bf7a-0890d8e5956c">
